{"title":"我望着你","date":"2018-04-18T15:49:44.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Apr 18, 2018","L":"04/18/2018","MM-DD":"04-18"},"thumbnail":"https://i.loli.net/2019/12/30/O9pMqfTikP5QLXy.jpg","link":"2018/04/18/我望着你","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-12-14T15:10:11.498Z","content":"<p>我痴然地望着你<br>\n阳光下温暖的草地<br>\n松软的土壤<br>\n泥土里混着迷乱的气息</p>\n<p>我望着你<br>\n你还是你</p>\n<p>我用力地拥抱着你<br>\n沐浴和煦的朝曦<br>\n伸进疏酥的泥土<br>\n放肆这自然的气息</p>\n<p>我抱着你<br>\n你的怀里不是你</p>\n","prev":{"title":"到站了","link":"2018/04/30/到站了"},"next":{"title":"只为再见到你","link":"2018/04/16/只为再见到你"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2018/04/18/我望着你/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Birch","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"December 14, 2020"},"reading_time":"79 words in 1 min"}